&lt;p&gt;This position will be a member of the WhiteWater accounting department in Austin. Responsible include assisting in daily cash accounting operations, preparing cash journal entries and reconciliations. This role helps in the execution of the company’s daily cash payment and receipt process, ensures accurate allocation of funds across multiple entities and accounts, and supports liquidity planning, and process improvement initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
