&lt;p&gt;This position is responsible for the maintenance and documentation of turbine engines on the BayRunner pipeline. The role is based in the Agua Dulce–Raymondville, TX area or within a 75-mile radius, reporting to the Alice, TX office.&lt;/p&gt;
